adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6fe7e0cc5cd0937151c5a8f5bdf9d194bdfc63","tid":2400790,"uid":345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:30:18.000Z","msg":"口交部啲氣焰去咗邊 <br />\n應該即刻拉鳩個記者嘛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323b595d8e388e903406309b5b6a1b820e87efa3","tid":2400790,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e6fe7e0cc5cd0937151c5a8f5bdf9d194bdfc63","tid":2400790,"uid":345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:30:18.000Z","msg":"口交部啲氣焰去咗邊 <br />\n應該即刻拉鳩個記者嘛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:38:50.000Z","msg":"好嬲<br />\n雖遠必豬"},{"pid":"9cb955511eabfd7ac6102012c7c8136d65eba11e","tid":2400790,"uid":342828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:50:38.000Z","msg":"南海下面會唔會已經無晒位，好似包龍星同豹頭、皇帝迫喺床下底咁？<br />\n大家咁緊張，真係有D八國聯軍feel。個個準備一有機會即刻上水插旗、落釘。"},{"pid":"617b6951eee479cf77dfab8a0c31604565bd458e","tid":2400790,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"點解美國就屌，法國就咁溫和呀，對呢啲所謂戰狼好失望囉"}]}